{"tid":2499941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發有感 以前既香港電影真係好敢講 （多圖）","createTime":"2021-04-22T09:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T09:15:08.000Z","uid":329289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8d613c68fa9dc94a9a95e66e3ec54c80446d4409","tid":2499941,"uid":329289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"前排突然想煲返啲舊戲黎睇<br />\n睇睇下發現差唔多套套戲都有講移民<br />\n九七回歸之前個個爭住走<br />\n共產黨殺到黎咩坦克車都夠膽死講<br />\n好多金句<br />\n依家拍部電影都可以吿你印假鈔<br />\n原來上一代人都知香港交返比中國就會冇好日子過<br />\n個個都想移民 根本同依家既情況一樣<br />\n歷史又重演<br />\n唔同既只係以前係白紙黑字寫到明要歸還香港比黨賊<br />\n依家蝗國擺明車馬強槍<br />\n真係好想好想香港有贏既一日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQjQ9Jz8thAu4cMrdiAg8kyTH3XWx8KE38r6TeNdgkSin?filename=YckVgMn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYckVgMn.png&h=020ba83a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmX2VNrsp35s2zHWXjdBqfQbTuMDTN96Yckh1Xk6ZvgNmA?filename=ccbmcjJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccbmcjJ.png&h=7f4fe360&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcwHk4nZEsZZN6uExHRaZD2rqiRuM2ELvLMPiMKCaHtCY?filename=dRcHGc5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRcHGc5.png&h=3366843d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdThNApEiGKperudFyKK2GqT47y818MwqTaGkZ3oywV5s?filename=1Txwzx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Txwzx6.png&h=cb24daff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfQ7k1fSmE3k1wdpEBiv263S9YVh8sCpQd9KYLM354p9A?filename=fvuu5H9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffvuu5H9.png&h=04a37360&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmP9AFqfcPwpPzcufY5pRVnADge7crZLGAwqGZ6C6AUupV?filename=vpoLD29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvpoLD29.png&h=0bfa4738&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io